               </h2>
              </div>
              <div class="views-field views-field-body">
               <div class="field-content">
                <p>
                 <a href="https://calendar.math.illinois.edu/">
                  Seminar and Event Calendar
                 </a>
                </p>
                <p>
                 <span>
                  <span>
                   <span>
                    <span>
                     <a href="https://faculty.math.illinois.edu/~hquan4/GSTGC2019/index.html">
                      17th Annual Graduate Student Topology and Geometry Conference
                     </a>
                    </span>
                    <span>
                     , March 30-31, 2019
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </span>
                 </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                 <a href="https://calendar.math.illinois.edu/?year=2019&amp;month=02&amp;day=13&amp;interval=year&amp;regexp=Mathematics+Colloquium+%2d%2d+Tondeur+Lectures+in+Mathematics&amp;use=Find">
                  Tondeur Lectures in Mathematics
                 </a>
                 , presented by André Neves (University of Chicago), April 9-11, 2019
                </p>
                <p>
                 <a href="/illinois-risk-lab/symposium">
                  Risk Analytics Mini-Symposium and Illinois Actuarial Science Reception
                 </a>
                 , May 16, 2019
                </p>
                <p>
                 <a href="/nt2019">
                  Analytic and Combinatorial Number Theory: The Legacy of Ramanujan
                 </a>
                 , June 6-9, 2019
                </p>
                <p>
                 <a href="/grow2019">
                  GROW (Graduate Research Opportunities for Women) 2019 Conference
                 </a>
                 , October 4-6, 2019
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
