                <div class="views-field views-field-title">
                 <h2 class="field-content">
                  Alumni Spotlight:
                  <a href="/spotlight/alumni/alumnus-creates-growing-program-enrich-math-abilities-underserved-children" hreflang="en">
                   Alumnus creates a growing program to enrich math abilities in underserved children
                  </a>
                 </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="views-field views-field-body">
                 <div class="field-content">
                  <p>
                   Since graduating from Illinois with two masters degrees, Daniel Zaharopol decided that the best use of his love of and training in mathematics was to open the mathematics community to underserved students.
                  </p>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div class="views-field views-field-view-node">
                 <span class="field-content button">
